Author: BEDBulimic
Text: My “meals” are all over the place- a hodge podge of fasting, planned processed junk b/p, ortho meals then turn to binges that turn to b/p, or normal traditional korean meals.  I’m actively trying to limit my purges to once a day max and no more than 3 days successively (otherwise my gag reflex dies and i bloat so much worse)  It’s hard though :/
